{"tid":1535253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以多謝罷工罷課嘅人?","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:55:09.000Z","uid":167277,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"860e37f7480880d763e54e9dade2270954bf3d55","tid":1535253,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:44:40.000Z","msg":"我明白呢兩日罷工對比起8月5號係少人好多<br />\n冇咁多大機構響應，職場又出現白色恐怖<br />\n加上早兩日好多新聞，分散左注意<br />\n但係今日仲有罷工嘅人，真係好有心架<br />\n仲有班學生呀! <br />\n可唔可以多謝佢地，讚下佢地？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c9af1498b0abdfefe46f3cc31b67c2a1059070","tid":1535253,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44f642c32ece801a63bbe6be596c9502231b1d67","tid":1535253,"uid":167277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"呢段日子好黑暗<br />\n我地互相鼓勵同支持 先可以一齊捱落去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959e9bcb4958561413e460fa7ae5c2100e5de96c","tid":1535253,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0200d84fa0911f94d8e60d4cb1391ba08bb286","tid":1535253,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368397e8181f6014088905ce756fdba638910735","tid":1535253,"uid":46314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) Twitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=0e165622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\nTwitter 英文/外語組 <a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=541c234a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"0633028c5d308c85764e8c50f8f28dbe613a25c8","tid":1535253,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"我明白今日少人係有原因<br />\n唔會怪任何人<br />\n但係都可以俾d支持罷左課 罷左工嘅手足掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f69e9e03169d3a2556fa67bd7447af06bc80b6","tid":1535253,"uid":276783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632b1dae512e4248b416bc7fc46040e67c9ccc2d","tid":1535253,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:12:27.000Z","msg":"要"},{"pid":"89c0dcc383512fa6e1def9095d9772ac7458390e","tid":1535253,"uid":97078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"多謝各位"},{"pid":"f5d60236dd4c37b20eb4e00b158f76cceedf2f7e","tid":1535253,"uid":20444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7237d215ba42fd055ed0dbccdf5bd819e13b61","tid":1535253,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5d60236dd4c37b20eb4e00b158f76cceedf2f7e","tid":1535253,"uid":20444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef4447c4a30dd0f5c605073acda93f5174edf60","tid":1535253,"uid":75745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"d34b6767a7071129f89be6add6afa51df731c102","tid":1535253,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime